{
  "stem": "12462.5",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Ley was head of the German labor front, which was the group which took over the free trade unions and made a kind of a inside company union, which-- in which people had no votes or anything like that.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But they paid their dues.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And as a result, they were allowed to travel, and were given vacation resorts, and things like that.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he was a very skilled propagandist, and had his own newspapers, and so forth.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I was making out a case against him as a part of the conspiracy for the destruction of the trade unions, and for building the German labor front, et cetera.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I had passed materials for his interrogation to both his counsel and to our interrogators before the trial began.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he wrote, in his cell, some responses to some of these things.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And after-- about eight days after he was indicted, he committed suicide in his cell.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Got back in a corner, sat on the toilet, tied a towel around his neck and on a fixture above him, and managed to strangle himself to death.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the guards who were passing by and looking in every now and then didn't notice this, until they noticed the-- that-- [STAMMERS] that they could just barely see his knees, or something.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It looked unnatural.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They opened the door, and there he was, dead.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So that was my first defendant.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, he-- that reduced the number of defendants by one.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Oh, I should say another one was dismissed just within two or three days before the trial.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that was Gustav Krupp.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He was found by representatives of the tribunal who went to serve the indictment on him to be in a senile state and utterly incapable of talking.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he was dying.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
